38:52.000 --> 38:53.240
Yeah, I understand.

38:53.480 --> 38:57.880
Proving what actually happened
is often impossible,

38:58.240 --> 39:00.960
so the best you can do is show

39:01.320 --> 39:04.520
that there's a reasonable doubt
about a person's guilt.

39:05.040 --> 39:07.480
It's rare that you could
prove somebody innocent.

39:08.720 --> 39:10.920
Sure, I want to know,
because it's a mystery,

39:11.000 --> 39:14.320
and we all want to know
how the mystery ends.

39:14.600 --> 39:15.880
What happened?

39:16.880 --> 39:21.680
I can completely understand Michael's
view of that, which is,

39:22.320 --> 39:27.280
"Hey, I lost the person in my life
who I loved the most,

39:28.040 --> 39:31.320
and that's the only thing that really
matters at the end of the day."

39:31.840 --> 39:35.640
But for the rest of us who are just
observers, who are not participants,

39:36.040 --> 39:37.920
we want to know what happened.

39:38.280 --> 39:42.200
If you ask me,
"What's the most likely scenario?"

39:42.600 --> 39:43.760
I'd say it's a fall.

39:44.000 --> 39:46.960
Can I rule out that it was an intruder?

39:47.720 --> 39:50.160
I can't. No one can.

39:50.720 --> 39:52.840
You can say there's no evidence of that.

39:54.040 --> 39:59.800
But it's well known that the absence
of evidence is not evidence of absence.

40:00.240 --> 40:01.920
So, we don't know.

40:03.000 --> 40:07.520
Can I say a hundred percent that it
wasn't some raptor who flew down

40:07.600 --> 40:10.040
and inflicted those scalp wounds

40:10.600 --> 40:14.320
without causing a skull fracture
or any brain injury?

40:14.400 --> 40:16.160
I can't say one way or the other.

40:21.960 --> 40:23.160
What to do?

40:24.560 --> 40:26.840
Oh, honey. Oh, no.

40:26.920 --> 40:28.080
Hello?

40:36.360 --> 40:37.440
Oh, God.

40:44.720 --> 40:46.560
Uh, from that moment, it's...

40:48.640 --> 40:50.000
it's really...

40:51.120 --> 40:53.480
hard because there was just blood.

40:54.400 --> 40:55.640
But I couldn't...

40:56.920 --> 40:59.680
I don't think I focused so much
on the blood.

41:00.160 --> 41:02.880
Certainly, at first,
the fact that she's lying there,

41:03.480 --> 41:06.240
uh, and I went and grabbed her,

41:06.640 --> 41:09.240
saw her and... uh...

41:11.000 --> 41:13.000
it was just...

41:17.480 --> 41:20.240
That was worse
than anything that I ever

41:20.840 --> 41:22.240
saw or did in war.

41:22.760 --> 41:26.720
And then I ran up and got some towels
to put under her head and whatnot.

41:27.320 --> 41:28.320
Uh...

41:29.160 --> 41:31.720
Called 911 or maybe I called 911 first.

41:31.800 --> 41:33.840
I'm sure I called 911 first,

41:34.400 --> 41:37.800
and said that
she's fallen down the stairs. Uh...

41:38.920 --> 41:40.400
Which is what I believed.

41:40.520 --> 41:43.040
She's at the bottom of the stairs.
Well, she fell.

41:43.160 --> 41:44.360
Uh...

41:45.360 --> 41:47.960
It was just this...

41:50.760 --> 41:54.320
I mean, it's such a cliche,
it's almost a euphemism.

41:54.400 --> 41:57.960
I was in shock. I was in shock.

41:58.320 --> 42:01.080
I just couldn't believe it.
We had just talked, we just...

42:01.440 --> 42:02.440
It was...

42:06.720 --> 42:10.040
No, it was much worse than war,
because in war, you expect things.

42:10.440 --> 42:13.400
I mean, I can remember,
during the Tet Offensive, you know?

42:13.720 --> 42:16.040
Terrible things happ--
Terrible things happened.

42:16.720 --> 42:19.120
But you expect terrible things
to happen in war.

42:19.200 --> 42:20.360
You're ready for that.

42:20.440 --> 42:23.280
You don't want it to happen.
When it happens, it's a shock,

42:23.440 --> 42:25.920
but nothing like this.

42:26.520 --> 42:27.560
Uh...

42:28.040 --> 42:32.000
Someone that you love,
you were just with, you know, they're...

42:32.240 --> 42:33.240
They're there.

42:33.480 --> 42:36.560
And she was dying. I knew that.
I could just tell that right away.

42:38.520 --> 42:43.000
And then I just don't really remember.

42:44.040 --> 42:46.640
I mean, I just remember activity.

42:46.720 --> 42:52.400
Sort of this white noise or white action
that's going on in back of--

42:52.560 --> 42:54.880
You know, people coming and going and...

42:55.040 --> 42:56.280
Uh...

42:57.840 --> 43:00.040
I don't know.
I guess it's the first time...

43:01.520 --> 43:02.680
maybe the only time...

43:04.520 --> 43:06.120
I guess it is the only time

43:06.400 --> 43:08.280
I've ever been just totally shocked

43:08.600 --> 43:10.600
and just not really...

43:13.520 --> 43:14.360
there.

43:14.600 --> 43:17.000
I mean, I went through
some terrible things in war,

43:17.320 --> 43:20.000
but you're trained for that.

43:20.080 --> 43:22.080
You know, you'd better call in
the artillery,

43:22.160 --> 43:24.840
you'd better call in a medivac,
you'd better do these things.

43:24.920 --> 43:28.760
You know,
you're trained to do these things because

43:29.960 --> 43:31.440
you know they can happen.

43:33.320 --> 43:36.200
But this was something that's just...

43:37.880 --> 43:39.600
I don't know. I mean, I was just,

43:40.240 --> 43:42.000
you know, nobody trains you for that.

43:42.120 --> 43:45.160
And I didn't, I didn't know what to do

43:45.240 --> 43:49.040
except call 911 and, thank God,

43:49.720 --> 43:52.000
uh, you know, Todd and, uh...

43:53.240 --> 43:55.000
What was her name? Lovely girl.

43:56.160 --> 43:59.320
Came within literally three
or four minutes.

43:59.600 --> 44:01.040
And, uh...

44:01.600 --> 44:04.640
And then after that it was just...
it was just crazy.

44:05.000 --> 44:09.360
So, that's all I can say.
I just remember being...

44:12.640 --> 44:14.920
I guess for the first time
in my life, just...

44:16.400 --> 44:17.920
totally, completely...

44:20.000 --> 44:21.720
overwhelmed, just shut down.

44:21.800 --> 44:23.000
This is not...

44:24.120 --> 44:25.240
It just wasn't...

44:31.960 --> 44:34.960
It just wasn't right. It just couldn't be.

44:35.840 --> 44:36.920
But it was.

44:38.000 --> 44:42.360
So, that's the best I can do,
is to tell you

44:43.200 --> 44:45.240
I saw her and...

44:47.440 --> 44:50.040
...I wasn't ready for that.

44:51.400 --> 44:52.280
At all.

